{"id": "1520725723160121424", "channel_id": "1520725723160121424", "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "content": "如果伟力仅仅是这个补偿幅度，那直接发回溯吧，真有点恶心人。而且新角色没上线就没了一个特别高上限的玩法，不用给补偿吗？\n伟力的削弱幅度：基础暴伤算到头就是248%（这需要你本身就是暴伤主属性的角色+12，还需要顶级密契，两个+12爆伤命轮），多5%转化就是12.4%而已。按照旧的算法，你任意角色带红茶命轮，开了红茶以后都能多传递12%暴伤，这还没算别的内容，这不是赤裸裸大削？别告诉你们完全没算过这种？", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T09:41:06.119000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520725723160121424", "reactions": [{"emoji": "😼", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1520725723390939246", "filename": "c326b66bebffce61653dd1e937eb93d4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 235399, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520725723160121424/1520725723390939246/c326b66bebffce61653dd1e937eb93d4.jpg?ex=6a423db2&is=6a40ec32&hm=039fe8e79ae3191a0524d25d5c7502e1b9d23364979f3efccf3744d66448090b&"}, {"id": "1520725723919159336", "filename": "d49fea400f94fe4b2b76c00591ab7ee1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 210452, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520725723160121424/1520725723919159336/d49fea400f94fe4b2b76c00591ab7ee1.jpg?ex=6a423db2&is=6a40ec32&hm=bc2ae7892b04103aacda68591445df2247b83e85a5ba3164832ead09906f4da1&"}]}
