{"id": "1520740636314042369", "channel_id": "1520725723160121424", "author_id": "1350802825357295638", "author_name": "caakssi", "content": "Oh wow, Pontos got nerfed before he even hit live servers? Looking at his kit now, he might as well crawl back into the corner.\nOk, let's be serious — Pontos needs a rework. He is not a standard unit. If he were, I'd shrug and say \"ok, maybe he needs AA to be good, fine, I can pull for that.\" But no — he's a LIMITED unit! HELLO?! I can't dump every resource I have just to make him playable with AA.\nAnd I'm not even asking for buffs or brand-new card effects. That's not the issue. The issue is that he doesn't work as a DPS, and he doesn't work as a support either. He just... doesn't work.\nHe needs a rework. Period.", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T10:40:21.692000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520725723160121424"}
