{"id": "1520897656111759504", "channel_id": "1520897656111759504", "author_id": "218561860553670656", "author_name": "kafziel6", "content": "I think at this point in the game the Devs should consider lowering the keeper level requirement for getting Ramona shards to bring her +12 timeline more inline with the other starter characters.  I even think it should be lowered to keeper level 60 and basically be treated as the f2p player introduction character to the AA system.\n\nI have been playing for almost 6 months and have been able to +12 Ogier, Lotan and Doll already. Meanwhile despite being a lite spender I am only keeper level 67 and am 6+ months away from +12 Ramona.", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T21:04:18.129000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520897656111759504"}
