{"id": "1520934444482171013", "channel_id": "1512185775452721233", "author_id": "714546325278031882", "author_name": "garbage6500", "content": "I have discovered the issue and managed to fix it.\nThe problem was that the Qookka login overlay is reliant on Microsoft Edge WebView2 to appear. Due to me having completely uninstalled Microsoft Edge years ago using a third-party tool, the WebView2 component was also disabled on my computer. I reverted this and was finally able to login and play the game.\n\nApologies for the false bug report, since it was technically my fault.", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T23:30:29.160000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1512185775452721233", "mentions": ["1470253170209853632"], "reply_to": "1512365742211727562"}
